---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us — Cold Email Checker"
  description="Learn about Cold Email Checker — a free tool that helps you write better cold emails by detecting spam trigger words and improving deliverability."
  keywords="about cold email checker, email deliverability tool, spam checker tool"
>
  <Navbar />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink">About Us</h1>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-body leading-relaxed">
      <p>Cold Email Checker is a free tool built to help marketers, sales teams, and founders improve their cold email deliverability.</p>

      <p>We know that getting emails into the inbox — not the spam folder — is one of the biggest challenges in outbound outreach. That's why we built a simple, fast, and privacy-respecting spam checker that analyzes your email content in real time.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink pt-4">How It Works</h2>
      <p>Our tool scans your email subject line and body for known spam trigger words and patterns. Everything is processed in your browser — we never see or store your email content.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink pt-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p>We believe cold email can be done ethically and effectively. Our mission is to give everyone access to the tools they need to write professional, deliverable emails — without paying for expensive platforms.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink pt-4">100% Free, No Sign-Up</h2>
      <p>Cold Email Checker is completely free to use with no registration required. Check as many emails as you want, anytime.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
